         <ab>DoHom1.3 (mss. 2000, 2035):</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            <em>haōmanąm uzdātanąm</em> čīyōn pēš nibišt hōmāst dudīgar bār guftan tā sar ka <em>vaca aršuxδa</em> tā sar guft zōt ud rāspīg <em>aṣ̌əm vohū</em> se</ab> 
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            "At <em>haōmanąm uzdātanąm</em>, they should recite a second time the Hōmāst until the end as it has been written. When they have recited <em>vaca aršuxδa</em> until the 
            end, the <em>zōt</em> and the <em>rāspīg</em> (should recite) three <em>Aṣ̌əm Vohū</em>."</ab>
      </Nerangs>
